10, 2006</font></p>
      <p align="left"><font face="Palatino, Book Antiqua, serif"><strong>For
Immediate Release</strong></font></p>
      <p align="left"><font face="Palatino, Book Antiqua, serif">For
more information, contact:<br>
Richard Groves&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
      </font><font face="Palatino, Book Antiqua, serif">Association of
Research Libraries<br>
